{"tid":1007571,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今朝遇著個ON9的士佬","createTime":"2019-02-04T00:48:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T10:50:46.000Z","uid":19386,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"75c7a2e3ea61e2c0060612863c0e7f8fb83a66b3","tid":1007571,"uid":19386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T00:48:36.000Z","msg":"今朝陪我媽媽去醫院做覆診，我都知係返工時間，我支單短途三十幾蚊，咁我都唔想架，媽媽要用助行架行路，行唔得遠。<br />\n<br />\n咁就截左架的士，屌你個司機全程西晒面，又勁大力拉支棍，去到醫院又唔撚停係醫院門口，停左係正門後30米，擺明玩野。<br />\n<br />\n我就死唔落車，叫佢渣去門口，佢就大大力踩油。<br />\n<br />\n擺車尾箱個助行架又想收我錢，喂呀叔渣左幾耐的士呀？助行架唔收得錢架，屌！<br />\n<br />\n乜撚野事呀？好撚嬲啊！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇人試過更加西既的士體驗？"},{"pid":"f4c074362e1ddf521fd999a31fcab95d9a3cd341","tid":1007571,"uid":182930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T00:51:32.000Z","msg":"DC9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8509c59f26a400897d38afd142d2cf851ca38f54","tid":1007571,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T00:53:19.000Z","msg":"太短程唔想車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a93cad958e8d1a9b34604f72c5b06d3c8813899a","tid":1007571,"uid":51701,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T00:54:11.000Z","msg":"講真DC全部都係9<br />\n<br />\n接call會好禮貌啲"},{"pid":"3cef521966be241558caecbcc23f84e6202a104b","tid":1007571,"uid":19386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a93cad958e8d1a9b34604f72c5b06d3c8813899a","tid":1007571,"uid":51701,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T00:54:11.000Z","msg":"講真DC全部都係9<br />\n<br />\n接call會好禮貌啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-0